name: Speakoutfreedom
tag_list: speak-out-freedom, social, blogging, network, articles, religion, politics, entertainment, world-news, free-blog, comment, debate, argue, reply
overview: Speakoutfreedom is a social blogging network that allows people to comment and debate on hot controversial topics in the world, as well as create a social network with other members of the site! Members sign up for free, create a custom personal profile, comment, reply and debate with other members on articles that are uploaded daily. Members are able to create their own personal blogs within the site for other members to comment on, or answer a question that has been asked. There is a personal page in the members profile for members to correspond back and forth socially within their network that they have created!
